  "body": "- [x] I've asked for help in the [Truffle Gitter](http://gitter.im/Consensys/truffle) before filing this issue.\r\n\r\n---------------------------\r\n\r\n## Issue\r\n\r\nWrong abi for `mapping(address => uint[])`\r\n\r\n## Steps to Reproduce\r\n\r\nCreate a contract with `mapping(address => uint[]) foo`.\r\n\r\n## Expected Behavior\r\n\r\nA getter exactly like this: `foo(address) returns (uint[])`\r\n\r\n## Actual Results\r\n\r\nA getter exactly like this: `foo(address, uint) returns (uint)`\r\n\r\nAnd this is the abi: \r\n\r\n```\r\n{\r\n  \"constant\": true,\r\n  \"inputs\": [\r\n    {\r\n      \"name\": \"\",\r\n      \"type\": \"address\"\r\n    },\r\n    {\r\n      \"name\": \"\",\r\n      \"type\": \"uint256\"\r\n    }\r\n  ],\r\n  \"name\": \"userToIds\",\r\n  \"outputs\": [\r\n    {\r\n      \"name\": \"\",\r\n      \"type\": \"uint256\"\r\n    }\r\n  ],\r\n  \"payable\": false,\r\n  \"stateMutability\": \"view\",\r\n  \"type\": \"function\"\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Environment\r\n\r\n* Operating System: Ubuntu 16.04\r\n* Ethereum client: Remix\r\n* Truffle version (`truffle version`): 4.1.13\r\n* node version (`node --version`): 8.11.3\r\n* npm version (`npm --version`): 5.6.0\r\n",
