    "body": "Hi @ferittuncer. It looks like this is just the way solc implements the getter for that case. \r\n\r\nFrom [Arrays](https://solidity.readthedocs.io/en/develop/types.html?highlight=accessor#arrays) section at the Solidity docs:\r\n\r\n> It is possible to mark arrays public and have Solidity create a getter. The numeric index will become a required parameter for the getter.\r\n\r\nMore discussion about this topic in #302, including a workaround :) \r\n\r\n",
